list all the files.

00:01:13.205 --> 00:01:15.830
If you're using a Mac or Linux,

00:01:15.830 --> 00:01:17.855
they both come with Unix shell.

00:01:17.855 --> 00:01:20.135
You don't have to
install Git Bash.

00:01:20.135 --> 00:01:23.555
Git Bash is only meant for
Windows operating system.

00:01:23.555 --> 00:01:26.300
If you're not used to
either of these tools,

00:01:26.300 --> 00:01:28.190
then obviously it
is always better to

00:01:28.190 --> 00:01:30.800
choose Git Bash over good cmd.

00:01:30.800 --> 00:01:32.150
