00:01:33.740 --> 00:01:36.290
you can also work on
Linux operating system

00:01:36.290 --> 00:01:38.930
at later point in
time, if you were to.

00:01:38.930 --> 00:01:41.390
The third option we have is get

00:01:41.390 --> 00:01:43.805
